xref: Inverse permutation: A072765. a(n) = A069770(A072766(n)). Also transpose of A072766, i.e. a(n) = A072766(A038722(n)). The upper triangular region: A072773. Projection functions are A072771 ('car') & A072772 ('cdr'). The sizes of the corresponding Catalan structures: A072768. The first row: A057548, the first column: A072795, diagonal: A083938. Cf. also A080300, A025581, A002262.
